{
  "stem": "21817.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "But it used to be a school was a headquarters from the German army.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "And we did all kinds of jobs, cleaning toilets, streets.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "Anything.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "They needed help, they had Jewish commanders.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "And, and I was over there for a while.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "Then I was transferred to Baranowitsche with, with a group of men.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "Because the German army was going east, but the highways were so bad that they used to use slave labor, human labor, actually.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "We were Jews and also they had prisoners of war already, that they used to cut the trees and lay it down parallel and and build the highway so the, so the heavy trucks could go through.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "And you know, it's almost built on a [INAUDIBLE] as a highway.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "You know, there's plenty-- it's wooded area those streets, those highways it used to go through.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "So we used to cut that tree on one side and on the other side to, lay it down to each other.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "Then you would put in dirt on top so the trucks could go through.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "And there were a lot of prisoners over there, Soviet prisoners or Russian prisoners.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "And also in, in the area were also a lot of dead people laying because they were fighting before over there with the Russian troops.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "And also there were big holes from bombs which exploded.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "And they used to-- we used to-- we had to take some of the human beings and pull them.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "[SOBBING] We used to pull those soldiers, dead soldiers, put them in in the big holes and cover them up.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "And then we had to go back to work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 81,
      "text": "They kept this for, for quite a while until we come to the main highways.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
